    "The beluga whale is a stocky and stout marine mammal that averages 3.5 to 5.5 m in length and weighs about 1500 kg.",
    "Belugas have keen vision and hearing, allowing them to swim and hunt in response to sounds.",
    "They also have a cheerful demeanor and graceful movements (Zhong et al. 2022).",
    "The BWO algorithm (Zhong et al. 2022) simulates beluga whale actions such as swimming, hunting, and falling.",
